M|kai|- **December**: 2× baseline traffic and conversion — plan ahead, benchmark separately
M|kai|- **January**: post-holiday drop; engagement recovers before revenue
M|kai|- **Fashion weeks** (Feb/Sep): organic reach spikes — capitalise on trending moments
M|kai|- Tier match: DTC fashion brands with similar follower count (within 5×)
M|kai|- Flag: never cite Nike, Zara (14M+) as gap benchmarks for early-stage brand
M|kai|- Instagram saves are a stronger purchase-intent signal than likes for fashion
M|kai|- cnt about craft/materials outperforms lifestyle cnt by ~40% avg engagement
M|kai|- UGC-style cnt on Meta converts 2:1 over polished creative
